street-art-2.jpg 148w,\n/blog/static/d69fd0cfcdb87ce7c724f62c4dacf7b2/1c91a/street-art-2.jpg 295w,\n/blog/static/d69fd0cfcdb87ce7c724f62c4dacf7b2/1c72d/street-art-2.jpg 590w,\n/blog/static/d69fd0cfcdb87ce7c724f62c4dacf7b2/a8a14/street-art-2.jpg 885w,\n/blog/static/d69fd0cfcdb87ce7c724f62c4dacf7b2/fbd2c/street-art-2.jpg 1180w,\n/blog/static/d69fd0cfcdb87ce7c724f62c4dacf7b2/12609/street-art-2.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/7c2eee0fd31a9e2bf74dfd458df9a66e/12609/street-art-3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"street-art-3\"\n        title=\"street-art-3\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/7c2eee0fd31a9e2bf74dfd458df9a66e/1c72d/street-art-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/7c2eee0fd31a9e2bf74dfd458df9a66e/a80bd/street-art-3.jpg 148w,\n/blog/static/7c2eee0fd31a9e2bf74dfd458df9a66e/1c91a/street-art-3.jpg 295w,\n/blog/static/7c2eee0fd31a9e2bf74dfd458df9a66e/1c72d/street-art-3.jpg 590w,\n/blog/static/7c2eee0fd31a9e2bf74dfd458df9a66e/a8a14/street-art-3.jpg 885w,\n/blog/static/7c2eee0fd31a9e2bf74dfd458df9a66e/fbd2c/street-art-3.jpg 1180w,\n/blog/static/7c2eee0fd31a9e2bf74dfd458df9a66e/12609/street-art-3.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>To make it easier to find the spots I've created a <a class=\"articleLink\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/edit?mid=1XD5OSGiUPT6XZbBuUgCKGyFmKnW50v73&usp=sharing\">Google map </a>where I've marked these as well as other of the places I recommend visiting while in Lyon.</p>\n<p>Enjoy!\n<br />\n<br /></p>\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\">\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1XD5OSGiUPT6XZbBuUgCKGyFmKnW50v73&ll=45.76635419222272%2C4.829192569836458&z=15\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></iframe>\n</div>\n<br />\n<hr>\n<p>If you are curious to know more about the history of Lyon's traboules I recommend listening to this 5 min long explanation.\n<br />\n<br /></p>\n<iframe src=\"https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/4cNhFh1T27BJlHtY002FCM?utm_source=generator&theme=0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"152\" frameBorder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture\"></iframe>","frontmatter":{"title":"Walking through the secret passageways/traboules in Lyon","tags":["travel","France","Lyon"],"categories":"travel","date":"January 08, 2022","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"src":"/blog/static/d7eaacb57ee53c132ab835460feca468/4fe8c/cover-traboules.jpg"}}}},"excerpt":"A few months ago I went on a solo weekend trip to Lyon. I booked a flight and a hotel and with no actual plan was ready for an adventure…","fields":{"slug":"/secret-passageways-Lyon/Walking through the secret passageways in Lyon/"},"timeToRead":3}},"pageContext":{}}}